pedal to the floor smash out ♪

01:20.706 --> 01:22.249
- Come on now. Right there.
Right there, man.

01:22.249 --> 01:23.458
- Yeah, man.

01:23.458 --> 01:25.669
- You got him.
- Hey!

01:25.669 --> 01:28.172
My bad to interrupt
but do you fools mind moving your car?

01:28.172 --> 01:29.464
I'm a little late for work.

01:29.464 --> 01:31.925
- Bad timing. We're in the middle
of an important race right now.

01:32.676 --> 01:34.678
- Yeah, it's Black versus Mexicans.

01:35.304 --> 01:36.638
- Hey, I'm Salvadorian.

01:36.638 --> 01:38.515
MAN:
Damn, all sensitive.

01:38.515 --> 01:39.683
♪ Look red ♪

01:39.683 --> 01:41.643
♪ Nigga, 'cause I'm hot, yeah,
shit done changed ♪

01:41.643 --> 01:42.728
